26) </div><div class="t m1c x5f he y678 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m12f x5a he y678 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m11a x46 he y10d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Beauty (Prov. 31:22, 25) </div><div class="t m1c x38 he y10d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m12f x5a he y10d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m719 x23 he y8bf ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How would you &quot;translate&quot; some of these, such as &quot;she selects wool </div><div class="t m70 x3f he y58f ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and flax&quot; (31:13), into today&apos;s daily life? </div><div class="t m68f x23 hf y591 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">All of the above are traits any person can have. Their rewards are </div><div class="t m327 x3f hf y592 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">great, for those who know such people call them blessed. Spouses of </div><div class="t m71a x3f hf y593 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such people praise them (Prov. 31:28, 29). Their example challenges </div><div class="t m71b x3f hf y8c0 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others, and their works bring honor to loved ones and to themselves. </div><div class="t m22f x3f hf y8c1 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Best of all, their life glorifies the God they love (Prov. 31:30). </div><div class="t m18c x77 he y597 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How should a Christian husband or wife act toward a harsh, </div><div class="t mce x55 he y8c2 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unkind, unbelieving spouse? </div><div class="t m652 x4e hf y1e0 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">101 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
